        },
        "has_children": false,
        "in_trash": false,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "paragraph": {
          "rich_text": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": {
                "content": "Authors create models using data from an Australian university and realize that sensitive attributes brought marginal gains to model performance and, when there is an increase in model effectiveness, it comes more of as a function of how the attribute is related to the target. ",
